## Reminder Triggers

### Automatic Triggers
- **When starting work that depends on a human task:**
  - Check for blocking tasks before starting dependent work
  - Remind user of prerequisite tasks
- **When a critical task is overdue:**
  - Remind daily for critical tasks pending > 3 days
  - Escalate reminder frequency for overdue critical tasks
- **At session start:**
  - Present summary of pending high/critical tasks
  - Show progress on in-progress tasks
- **When task status changes:**
  - Acknowledge completed tasks
  - Update reminders for status changes

### Context-Aware Triggers
- **Before security-related work:**
